<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="forget-v">forget <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /fə'ɡet/    美 /fər'ɡet/  </p>
<p>(forgot, forgotten)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>忘记；遗忘：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>forget about</strong> the key 
忘记带钥匙</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You'd better write down her phone number <strong>before you forget it</strong>.
你最好把她的电话号码记下来，以免忘记。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>forget doing sth 忘记做过某事：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I shall never forget watching the sunrise over the sea —it was unforgettable!
我永远不会忘记观看海上日出的情景——那一幕真是令人难忘！</p><footer>外研⑦ – 2</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>forget to do sth 忘记要做某事：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Teenagers live very busy lives and often forget to think about their diets and exercise.
青少年过着繁忙的生活，常常不注意他们的饮食和锻炼。</p><footer>译林① – 3</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>forget + (that) / wh-从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I will never forget what the experience has really taught me.
我永远不会忘记那次经历给我的真正教训。</p><footer>2014 天津</footer></div>

<h3 id="forget-leave">辨析 forget, leave</h3>
<p><strong>forget</strong> 意为“忘记”，常用forget (about) sth,forget doing sth, “forget + that / wh- 从句” 句型。
<strong>leave</strong> 也可表示“忘记”，但常和地点状语搭配使用，意为“把 (某物) 遗留在 (某处)”。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As soon as I shut the door, I realized I'd left the keys inside.
门关上的一瞬间，我意识到我把钥匙落在房间里了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>不再想；不再把...放在心上：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Try to <strong>forget about</strong> what happened.
尽量不要想已发生的事情。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let's forget our difference and be friends.
咱们别把分歧放在心上，做朋友吧。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="forget-it">forget it</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>没关系；不必在意：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Sorry, Liz. I think I was a bit rude to you.
很抱歉，利兹，我想我刚才对你有些无礼。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Forget it, but don't do that again!
没关系，但下不为例！</p><footer>2015 天津</footer></div>

<p>2.<strong>休想；不可能：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— I'd like to take a week's holiday.
我想休一周假。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Forget it; we're too busy.
不可能，我们太忙了。</p></div>

<p>3.<strong>别提了：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— What were you saying about John?
你刚才说约翰什么来着？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Forget it; it doesn't matter.
别提了，那无关紧要。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>— I'm sorry for breaking the cup. 
— Oh, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ — I've got plenty.   （2014 全国）<br />
A.forget it<br />
B.my pleasure<br />
C.help yourself<br />
D.pardon me  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. A  </p></div>